sections.body:
A  receipt from an employer-financed retirement benefits scheme which is otherwise chargeable under Section 394 ITEPA 2003 (see [EIM15015](/guidance/employment-income-manual/EIM15000#EIM15015) and [EIM15120](/guidance/employment-income-manual/EIM15000#EIM15120)) may nevertheless be excluded from charge.

For further information, see the general comments at [EIM15015](/guidance/employment-income-manual/EIM15000#EIM15015), the guidance for prior employer contributions at [EIM15125](/guidance/employment-income-manual/EIM15000#EIM15125) and [EIM15128](/guidance/employment-income-manual/EIM15000#EIM15128): and for prior employee contributions at [EIM15126](/guidance/employment-income-manual/EIM15000#EIM15126)&#xA0;

For examples see [EIM15329](/guidance/employment-income-manual/EIM15000#EIM15329).
